---
// Closing call to action — drives into the live demo. Footer is rendered by Layout below this.
---
<section class="final">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="panel">
      <h2>Vote in the shadows.<br /><span class="gradient-text">Execute in the light.</span></h2>
      <p>Cast a real sealed vote, then watch an autonomous agent carry it out on-chain — live on Stellar testnet, no recording.</p>
      <div class="cta">
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/demo/fund">Cast a sealed vote <span aria-hidden="true">→</span></a>
        <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/docs">Read the SDK docs</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .final { padding: clamp(3rem, 8vw, 6rem) 0 1rem; }
  .panel {
    position: relative; text-align: center; padding: clamp(2.4rem, 6vw, 4.5rem) 1.5rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: calc(var(--radius) + 4px); overflow: hidden;
    background:
      radial-gradient(60% 120% at 50% -10%, rgba(139,124,255,0.16), transparent 60%),
      radial-gradient(60% 120% at 50% 110%, rgba(61,224,230,0.12), transparent 60%),
      linear-gradient(180deg, var(--panel), var(--panel-2));
  }
  .panel h2 { margin: 0 0 0.7rem; }
  .panel p { color: var(--mist); max-width: 52ch; margin: 0 auto 1.8rem; }
  .cta { display: flex; gap: 0.8rem; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
</style>
